          "source": "def nsObj = ctx['cloudwatch_rum']; if (nsObj == null || nsObj.isEmpty()) return; if (ctx.aws == null) ctx.aws = new HashMap(); def svc = ctx.aws.containsKey('cloudwatch_rum') ? ctx.aws.get('cloudwatch_rum') : new HashMap(); for (def entry : nsObj.entrySet()) {   if (entry.getKey().equals('parsed')) continue;   if (!svc.containsKey(entry.getKey())) {     svc.put(entry.getKey(), entry.getValue());   } } ctx.aws.put('cloudwatch_rum', svc);",
